    <a href="/conversion-calculators/">Conversion Calculators</a> &rsaquo;
    <span>Weight Converter</span>
  </nav>
  <p class="last-updated">Last updated March 2026</p>
  <h1>Weight Converter</h1>
  <p class="page-desc">Convert between milligrams, grams, kilograms, metric tons, ounces, pounds, and stones instantly.</p>

  <div class="calculator-box">
    <div class="converter-area">
